{"tid":1959341,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼港 : 疫情促使企業增聘I.T狗 800個職位收9000份申請","createTime":"2020-04-05T10:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T18:04:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b064aa74cf7ca2112fa90c8a6fe9244db96b685e","tid":1959341,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"數碼港網上招聘博覽職位空缺及求職者創歷屆紀錄<br />\n05.04.2020 18:24<br />\n<br />\n數碼港表示，一年一度的招聘博覽因疫情移師網上進行，但參與公司、職位空缺及求職者人數都打破歷屆紀錄，反映疫情促使企業加快數碼轉型步代，會積極考慮明年實體及虛擬招聘博覽並行。<br />\n<br />\n數碼港指，為期兩日的博覽，有3000名求職者參與，提供的800個職位接獲逾9000份申請，當中近三成求職者具研究生或博士學歷。空缺中以業務拓展類工程最受歡迎，例如商業分析師、項目經理及市場推廣等，佔申請總數六成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278876&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278876%26csid%3D261_341&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=9fd70c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278876&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"3e6acfa98f059a9cb16762765a2c5e5e721d223b","tid":1959341,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9298c7d05c1ca184a8b98e81bddf5821f332d608","tid":1959341,"uid":47635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28438bfacacfb23d178ebf2daedcdd7e4ab57219","tid":1959341,"uid":64172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"Push 利申cs fg 冇報 cyberport工"},{"pid":"c7917af222266d6923d13c60bf0199d558e17a21","tid":1959341,"uid":6504,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"28438bfacacfb23d178ebf2daedcdd7e4ab57219","tid":1959341,"uid":64172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"Push 利申cs fg 冇報 cyberport工"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:33:04.000Z","ms